{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"URLSearchParams.get()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/get","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URL_API\">URL API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/append\"><code>append()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/delete\"><code>delete()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/entries\"><code>entries()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/forEach\"><code>forEach()</code></a></li><li><em><code>get()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/getAll\"><code>getAll()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/has\"><code>has()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/keys\"><code>keys()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/set\"><code>set()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/sort\"><code>sort()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/toString\"><code>toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/values\"><code>values()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for URL API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>URL</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams</code></a> 接口的<strong>get()</strong>方法返回第一个与搜索参数对应的值<strong>。</strong></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">URLSearchParams.get(name)</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"键名\">键名</dt>\n <dd>将要返回的参数的键名。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>返回一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb\"><code>USVString</code></a> ；如果没找到，返回&nbsp;<code><strong>null</strong></code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>如果一个页面的 URL 是&nbsp;<code>https://example.com/?name=Jonathan&amp;age=18</code>&nbsp;，你可以这样解析参数“name”和“age”:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"default prettyprint prettyprinted notranslate\"><code>let params = new URLSearchParams(document.location.search.substring(1));\nlet name = params.get(\"name\"); // is the string \"Jonathan\"\nlet age = parseInt(params.get(\"age\"), 10); // is the number 18</code>\n</pre>\n\n<p>查找一个不存在的键名则返回&nbsp;<code><strong>null</strong></code>:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\"><code>let address = params.get(\"address\"); // null</code></pre>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-urlsearchparams-get","title":"URL Standard"}],"query":"api.URLSearchParams.get"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.URLSearchParams.get","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/get/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"URLSearchParams 接口的get()方法返回第一个与搜索参数对应的值。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"URLSearchParams.get()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"URLSearchParams.get()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"URLSearchParams.get()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"URLSearchParams.get()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/urlsearchparams/get","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/urlsearchparams/get/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams","title":"URLSearchParams"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams/get","title":"URLSearchParams.get()"}],"pageTitle":"URLSearchParams.get() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}